  <brief_title>Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacodynamic Effects of Sublingual Immunotherapy (Tablets) With Recombinant Bet v1</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I Study to Investigate the Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacodynamic Effects of SLIT(Tablets) With Recombinant Bet v1 Given in Single Rising Doses and in Higher Multi Dose Regimens to Subjects Sensitised to Birch Pollen</official_title>
