  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the safety and tolerability of successive single rising doses of SLIT in
      subjects with allergic rhinitis and to investigate the safety and tolerability of multi high
      dose regimens of SLIT in subjects with allergic rhinitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
