  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  written consent

          -  Symptoms of birch pollen induced allergic rhinitis for at least the last 2 years.

          -  Sensitisation to birch pollen as demonstrated with a positive SPT to birch pollen and
             specific IgE level (birch pollen and r Bet v1) of at least Class 2 at screening.

          -  FEV1 at least of 80% of predicted values at screening.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient who previously received desensitization treatment to birch pollen and/or other
             betulaceae (e.g., hazel tree, alder…) or who plan to start desensitization treatment
             during this study.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
